==危险性==
XeO<sub>3</sub> 应该非常小心地处理，因为样品在室温下随时发生爆炸。干的三氧化氙晶体与纤维素发生爆炸性反应。<ref name="xe"/><ref>{{Cite journal | doi = 10.1126/science.139.3554.506 | title = Xenon Hydroxide: an Experimental Hazard | year = 1963 | last1 = Bartlett | first1 = N. | last2 = Rao | first2 = P. R. | journal = Science | volume = 139 | issue = 3554| pages = 506 | pmid = 17843880|bibcode = 1963Sci...139..506B }}</ref>

